title: Shihon Shugi no Seishin - Der Geist des Kapitarismus
description: Sayuri is a hard-working OL, the unsung heroine of Japan’s modern economy. With the help of her horny colleague Keiko and eager understudy Mayu-tan, the girls will lower office stress and keep spirits high...and make their way to another year of record profitability for the company!
